[Perhaps the most revealing statement is Dr. Fukuda's comment that:
"Public perceptions of the H1N1 pandemic have been strongly influenced
by the 5-year history of worry about the deadly H5N1 avian influenza
virus. Adjusting public perceptions to suit a far less lethal virus
has been problematic." - Mod.CP]

